Hāymānota ʾabaw, Synodal letter
     from Philotheus , patriarch of Alexandria to Dionysius III ( Athanasius IV of Antioch ?),
     patriarch of Antioch

Miracle of Mary: When Sǝfǝngǝyā, wife of king Masfǝyānos
     of Romǝyā, prays to have a child before the icon of St Mary, the icon inclines its head;
     Sǝfǝngǝyā then conceives Yǝsḥaq (ʾAbbā Garimā)

Miracle of Mary: The Ark of Zion is installed in ʾAksum;
     the coming there of ʾAbbā Salāmā, who explains to the priests attending the Ark its true
     significance
